name: Hamilton Gold Producer YIELD MAXIMIZER TM ETF
longDescription: The Fund investing in an equal-weight large-cap equity portfolio of gold producers domiciled,listed primarily in Canada and the United States. AMAX may also hold cash and cash equivalents or other money market instruments in order to meet its obligations The investment objective of AMAX is to deliver attractive monthly income.
